IN THE FLORIDA KEYS, OFFICIALS

09:01.107 --> 09:02.442
ARE CONSIDERING USING A DRAMATIC

09:02.442 --> 09:03.843
NEW APPROACH-- RELEASING

09:03.843 --> 09:06.179
GENETICALLY-MODIFIED MOSQUITOES

09:06.179 --> 09:07.747
TO KILL OFF THE SPECIES THAT

09:07.747 --> 09:09.082
CARRY DENGUE.

09:09.082 --> 09:10.250
THE LAB-GROWN MOSQUITOES HAVE

09:10.250 --> 09:11.985
BEEN TESTED IN BRAZIL AND IN THE

09:11.985 --> 09:13.853
CAYMAN ISLANDS, BUT MANY KEYS

09:13.853 --> 09:15.622
RESIDENTS WORRY THAT THEY WILL

09:15.622 --> 09:16.890
BE LIVING IN THE MIDDLE OF AN

09:16.890 --> 09:18.358
ONGOING EXPERIMENT.

09:18.358 --> 09:19.259
THE NEWSHOUR'S STEPHEN FEE

09:19.259 --> 09:22.662
REPORTS FROM FLORIDA.

09:22.662 --> 09:23.696
>> Reporter: KEY WEST IS A PLACE

09:23.696 --> 09:25.198
WHERE PEOPLE GENERALLY COME TO

09:25.198 --> 09:27.000
RELAX, AND THE DRAW'S PRETTY

09:27.000 --> 09:29.402
OBVIOUS-- WHITE SAND BEACHES,

09:29.402 --> 09:30.904
QUAINT ARCHITECTURE, THE

09:30.904 --> 09:32.672
WILDLIFE.

09:32.672 --> 09:34.374
BUT RELAXING ISN'T ON JESSICA

09:34.374 --> 09:36.676
BROWN'S AGENDA TODAY; SHE'S A

09:36.676 --> 09:38.311
FIELD INSPECTOR WITH THE FLORIDA

09:38.311 --> 09:40.880
KEYS MOSQUITO CONTROL DISTRICT.

09:40.880 --> 09:42.182
AND SINCE IT RAINED YESTERDAY,

09:42.182 --> 09:43.283
SHE'S GOT HER WORK CUT OUT FOR

09:43.283 --> 09:43.917
HER.

09:43.917 --> 09:46.119
>> GARBAGE CANS, AS LONG AS

09:46.119 --> 09:47.720
THEY'RE TURNED OVER, THEY'LL BE

09:47.720 --> 09:48.455
GOOD.

09:48.455 --> 09:49.122
>> Reporter: THERE ARE 45

09:49.122 --> 09:51.090
SPECIES OF MOSQUITO THAT THRIVE

09:51.090 --> 09:54.260
IN THE OFTEN-HUMID FLORIDA KEYS.

09:54.260 --> 09:55.762
BROWN'S JOB: PECK AROUND

09:55.762 --> 09:57.564
PEOPLES' BACKYARDS, CLEAR OUT

09:57.564 --> 09:59.265
STANDING WATER AND USE TINY

09:59.265 --> 10:01.935
PELLETS AND EVEN LARVAE-GOBBLING

10:01.935 --> 10:04.404
FISH TO KILL MOSQUITOES BEFORE

10:04.404 --> 10:06.306
THEY TURN INTO ADULTS.

10:06.306 --> 10:07.207
>> SO, MOSQUITOES COULD,

10:07.207 --> 10:09.242
DEPENDING ON HOW LONG THE WATER

10:09.242 --> 10:12.145
SITS, LAY THEIR EGGS, AND HAVE A

10:12.145 --> 10:13.913
REALLY BIG PROBLEM.

10:13.913 --> 10:14.681
>> Reporter: HER WORK'S PART OF

10:14.681 --> 10:17.150
A $10 MILLION A YEAR EFFORT BY

10:17.150 --> 10:18.418
THE KEYS MOSQUITO CONTROL

10:18.418 --> 10:20.386
DISTRICT, WHICH COVERS ALL OF

10:20.386 --> 10:21.988
MONROE COUNTY IN SOUTHERN

10:21.988 --> 10:24.257
FLORIDA, TO KILL OFF AS MANY OF

10:24.257 --> 10:26.092
THE FLYING BLOODSUCKERS AS

10:26.092 --> 10:27.760
POSSIBLE BECAUSE THEY'RE NOT

10:27.760 --> 10:29.462
JUST A NUISANCE.

10:29.462 --> 10:30.864
>> HEALTH OFFICIALS FIND 39

10:30.864 --> 10:32.198
CASES OF DENGUE FEVER IN THE

10:32.198 --> 10:33.299
KEYS.

10:33.299 --> 10:34.868
>> Reporter: IN 2009, AN

10:34.868 --> 10:36.536
OUTBREAK OF A MOSQUITO-BORNE

10:36.536 --> 10:38.972
DISEASE CALLED DENGUE FEVER

10:38.972 --> 10:41.174
STRUCK THE FLORIDA KEYS, THE

10:41.174 --> 10:42.709
FIRST LOCAL RESURGENCE OF THE

10:42.709 --> 10:45.445
VIRUS SINCE THE 1940s.

10:45.445 --> 10:46.779
>> DENGUE'S REALLY NASTY WHEN

10:46.779 --> 10:47.580
YOU GET IT.

10:47.580 --> 10:48.882
YOU KNOW, YOU GET A HIGH FEVER.

10:48.882 --> 10:51.217
YOU GET A RASH ALL OVER.

10:51.217 --> 10:52.051
BONE PAIN.

10:52.051 --> 10:53.353
THEY CALL IT "BREAK BONE FEVER"

10:53.353 --> 10:54.888
BECAUSE IT HURTS SO BAD.

10:54.888 --> 10:55.455
>> Reporter: THERE WERE A FEW

10:55.455 --> 10:57.657
DOZEN CASES AND NO FATALITIES,

10:57.657 --> 10:58.892
BUT THE OUTBREAK PROMPTED

10:58.892 --> 11:00.960
MOSQUITO CONTROL OFFICIALS IN

11:00.960 --> 11:02.662
THE KEYS TO CONSIDER AN

11:02.662 --> 11:04.364
EXPERIMENT THAT'S NEVER BEEN

11:04.364 --> 11:06.699
TRIED IN THE U.S. BEFORE--

11:06.699 --> 11:08.501
RELEASING POTENTIALLY MILLIONS

11:08.501 --> 11:09.602
OF GENETICALLY-MODIFIED

11:09.602 --> 11:12.171
MOSQUITOES TO KILL THE SPECIES

11:12.171 --> 11:14.040
THAT CARRIES DENGUE AND OTHER

11:14.040 --> 11:15.875
DANGEROUS DISEASES.

11:15.875 --> 11:17.076
BUT THE IDEA OF GENETICALLY-

11:17.076 --> 11:19.512
MODIFIED BUGS FLYING AROUND THIS

11:19.512 --> 11:20.713
TRADITIONALLY FIERCELY

11:20.713 --> 11:22.582
INDEPENDENT COMMUNITY HAS MANY

11:22.582 --> 11:24.217
RESIDENTS IN THE KEYS UP IN

11:24.217 --> 11:25.318
ARMS.

11:25.318 --> 11:26.686
>> WE ARE HUMANS, AND WE DON'T

11:26.686 --> 11:28.288
LIKE BEING TREATED LIKE GUINEA

11:28.288 --> 11:28.988
PIGS.

11:28.988 --> 11:29.822
>> Reporter: PUBLIC MEETINGS

11:29.822 --> 11:31.424
HERE IN THE KEYS HAVE EXPOSED A

11:31.424 --> 11:33.560
DEEP DIVIDE BETWEEN MOSQUITO

11:33.560 --> 11:35.528
CONTROL OFFICIALS AND SOME

11:35.528 --> 11:37.030
RESIDENTS WHO WORRY THAT THE

11:37.030 --> 11:38.998
GENETICALLY MODIFIED-- OR G.M.--

11:38.998 --> 11:40.800
MOSQUITOES COULD SOMEHOW MAKE

11:40.800 --> 11:41.968
THEM SICK.

11:41.968 --> 11:45.505
>> I AM BEING TOLD WHAT TO DO.

11:45.505 --> 11:47.407
>> Reporter: IS THERE ANY RISK

11:47.407 --> 11:48.408
TO MY HEALTH IF I GET STUNG BY A

11:48.408 --> 11:49.509
MOSQUITO WITH A GENETIC

11:49.509 --> 11:50.476
MODIFICATION LIKE THIS?

11:50.476 --> 11:51.711
>> THERE'S NO EVIDENCE OF ANY

11:51.711 --> 11:53.179
RISK AT ALL AT THIS POINT.

11:53.179 --> 11:54.080
>> Reporter: BUT "NO EVIDENCE OF

11:54.080 --> 11:54.948
RISK" IS DIFFERENT FROM THE

11:54.948 --> 11:56.416
PRESENCE OF RISK, RIGHT?

11:56.416 --> 11:58.518
>> TRUE, TRUE.

11:58.518 --> 11:59.285
>> Reporter: MICHAEL DOYLE IS

11:59.285 --> 12:01.054
EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR OF THE KEYS

12:01.054 --> 12:03.089
MOSQUITO CONTROL DISTRICT AND

12:03.089 --> 12:04.791
SAYS THE RISK OF DENGUE FEVER

12:04.791 --> 12:07.393
FAR OUTWEIGHS ANY RISKS FROM

12:07.393 --> 12:09.562
GENETICALLY MODIFIED MOSQUITOES.

12:09.562 --> 12:10.897
>> THE LAST THING WE WANT PEOPLE

12:10.897 --> 12:11.898
TO DO IS TO BE CONCERNED ABOUT

12:11.898 --> 12:12.832
COMING DOWN HERE AND GETTING

12:12.832 --> 12:14.033
SOMETHING.

12:14.033 --> 12:14.801
AND SO, WE'RE DOING EVERYTHING

12:14.801 --> 12:15.835
WE CAN TO MAKE SURE THAT NEVER

12:15.835 --> 12:16.569
HAPPENS.

12:16.569 --> 12:17.236
>> Reporter: THE MOSQUITOES THAT

12:17.236 --> 12:19.372
CARRY DENGUE FEVER, CALLED AEDES

12:19.372 --> 12:21.908
AEGYPTI, ARE TOUGH TO KILL.

12:21.908 --> 12:22.942
THEY'RE IMMUNE TO MANY

12:22.942 --> 12:24.744
INSECTICIDES AND BREED IN

12:24.744 --> 12:26.679
SOMETIMES HARD TO REACH PLACES,

12:26.679 --> 12:28.448
LIKE UNDERNEATH HOUSES OR IN THE

12:28.448 --> 12:29.649
LEAVES OF PLANTS LIKE

12:29.649 --> 12:30.717
BROMELIADS.

12:30.717 --> 12:32.385
SO, INSTEAD OF SPRAYS OR PELLETS

12:32.385 --> 12:34.354
THAT DON'T REACH THOSE PLACES,

12:34.354 --> 12:35.855
OFFICIALS IN THE KEYS TURNED TO

12:35.855 --> 12:39.158
A U.K. FIRM CALLED OXITEC.

12:39.158 --> 12:40.426
THEIR SCIENTISTS HAVE DEVELOPED

12:40.426 --> 12:41.794
A METHOD TO ALTER THE

12:41.794 --> 12:43.329
MOSQUITOES' GENETIC CODE TO KILL

12:43.329 --> 12:45.465
THEM OFF, OR AT LEAST KILL LOTS

12:45.465 --> 12:46.199
OF THEM.

12:46.199 --> 12:48.101
>> WE'VE INSERTED TWO GENES INTO

12:48.101 --> 12:49.636
THIS MOSQUITO.

12:49.636 --> 12:50.903
ONE GENE IS A SELF LIMITING

12:50.903 --> 12:53.006
GENE, AND THE OTHER GENE IS A

12:53.006 --> 12:54.340
MARKER.

12:54.340 --> 12:56.409
NOW, THE MARKER CAN IDENTIFY

12:56.409 --> 12:59.445
WHERE THESE GENES ARE INSERTED,

12:59.445 --> 13:02.982
AND THE OTHER ONE IS THE ONE

13:02.982 --> 13:04.784
THAT CAUSES THE OFFSPRING TO

13:04.784 --> 13:05.652
DIE.

13:05.652 --> 13:06.819
>> Reporter: SCIENTIST DERRIC

13:06.819 --> 13:09.222
NIMMO OVERSEES OXITEC'S PROPOSED

13:09.222 --> 13:11.157
KEYS TRIAL.

13:11.157 --> 13:12.258
HE AND HIS COLLEAGUES ARE ABLE

13:12.258 --> 13:14.327
TO TINKER WITH THE GENES OF MALE

13:14.327 --> 13:15.495
MOSQUITOES.

13:15.495 --> 13:17.363
>> THOSE MALES HAVE ONE JOB.

13:17.363 --> 13:18.898
THEY GO AND FIND A FEMALE, AND

13:18.898 --> 13:20.633
THEY PASS ON THEIR GENES.

13:20.633 --> 13:21.934
AND THEY PASS ON THE OXITEC GENE

13:21.934 --> 13:23.636
ALONG WITH THEIR OWN GENES.

13:23.636 --> 13:25.104
NOW, THE OFFSPRING THAT INHERIT

13:25.104 --> 13:27.540
THOSE GENES, THEY DIE.

13:27.540 --> 13:28.641
AND IF YOU RELEASE ENOUGH OF THE

13:28.641 --> 13:29.942
OXITEC MALES OVER A LONG ENOUGH

13:29.942 --> 13:32.045
PERIOD OF TIME, YOU CAN GET A

13:32.045 --> 13:33.046
CRASH OF THE MOSQUITO

13:33.046 --> 13:34.080
POPULATION.

13:34.080 --> 13:35.281
>> Reporter: OXITEC SAYS THEIR

13:35.281 --> 13:36.883
METHOD IS BOTH EFFECTIVE AND

13:36.883 --> 13:37.884
SAFE.

13:37.884 --> 13:39.419
THEY'VE CONDUCTED SMALL STUDIES

13:39.419 --> 13:41.320
IN THE CAYMAN ISLANDS, BRAZIL

13:41.320 --> 13:43.189
AND PANAMA-- PLACES WHERE DENGUE

13:43.189 --> 13:46.059
IS ENDEMIC-- AND WERE ABLE TO

13:46.059 --> 13:47.660
REDUCE THE POPULATION OF

13:47.660 --> 13:49.362
MOSQUITOES THAT CAN CARRY

13:49.362 --> 13:50.496
DENGUE.

13:50.496 --> 13:51.731
AND THEY SAY THOSE EXPERIMENTS

13:51.731 --> 13:53.966
DIDN'T HARM ANYONE.

13:53.966 --> 13:55.401
WITH THAT IN MIND, THE FIVE

13:55.401 --> 13:56.436
ELECTED MOSQUITO CONTROL

13:56.436 --> 13:58.604
OFFICIALS IN THE KEYS DECIDED TO

13:58.604 --> 14:00.973
PURSUE THEIR OWN G.M. MOSQUITO

14:00.973 --> 14:03.009
EXPERIMENT IN THE SMALL ISLAND

14:03.009 --> 14:05.378
NEIGHBORHOOD OF KEY HAVEN.

14:05.378 --> 14:07.013
AND OXITEC AGREED TO CONDUCT THE

14:07.013 --> 14:09.282
TRIAL FOR FREE, A TRIAL THAT HAS

14:09.282 --> 14:10.917
YET TO BEGIN.

14:10.917 --> 14:11.851
INITIALLY, FLORIDA KEYS

14:11.851 --> 14:14.153
BUSINESSPERSON MILA DE MIER SAYS

14:14.153 --> 14:16.522
THAT ALL SOUNDED GREAT TO HER.

14:16.522 --> 14:17.724
>> I SAY, "WOW, THIS IS

14:17.724 --> 14:18.491
FANTASTIC!

14:18.491 --> 14:19.826
THIS IS A REALLY, REALLY GREAT

14:19.826 --> 14:21.027
IDEA.

14:21.027 --> 14:22.161
BE ABLE TO FIGHT MOSQUITOES WITH

14:22.161 --> 14:23.696
ANOTHER MOSQUITOES?

14:23.696 --> 14:25.498
WHAT A GREAT CONCEPT!"

14:25.498 --> 14:26.499
AND, OBVIOUSLY, I DON'T LIKE

14:26.499 --> 14:27.967
MOSQUITOES BITING MY KIDS OR MY

14:27.967 --> 14:29.302
DOGS.

14:29.302 --> 14:30.336
>> Reporter: BUT DE MIER SAYS

14:30.336 --> 14:31.804
THE MORE SHE CONSIDERED IT, SHE

14:31.804 --> 14:34.006
FELT THE SCIENCE WAS TOO NEW,

14:34.006 --> 14:35.475
AND NOT ENOUGH WAS KNOWN FOR HER

14:35.475 --> 14:37.243
TO FEEL COMFORTABLE WITH G.M.

14:37.243 --> 14:38.945
MOSQUITOES IN HER COMMUNITY,

14:38.945 --> 14:40.747
DESPITE OXITEC'S SAFETY

14:40.747 --> 14:42.148
ASSURANCES.

14:42.148 --> 14:43.249
DE MIER STARTED AN ONLINE

14:43.249 --> 14:44.784
PETITION AGAINST THE MOSQUITO

14:44.784 --> 14:47.353
TRIAL THAT'S GATHERED 150,000

14:47.353 --> 14:48.621
SIGNATURES FROM AROUND THE

14:48.621 --> 14:49.455
WORLD.

14:49.455 --> 14:51.257
>> I DO NOT WANT MY KIDS TO BE

14:51.257 --> 14:52.658
LABORATORY RATS.

14:52.658 --> 14:53.960
I DON'T WANT MY KIDS TO BE

14:53.960 --> 14:55.261
GUINEA PIGS.

14:55.261 --> 14:56.496
WHY?

14:56.496 --> 14:58.131
BECAUSE THIS IS A BRAND NEW

14:58.131 --> 14:59.565
TECHNOLOGY.

14:59.565 --> 15:00.666
YOU GET THESE MOSQUITOES, YOU

15:00.666 --> 15:02.368
RELEASE ONCE AND FOR ALL, AND

15:02.368 --> 15:04.470
THEN LET'S EXPERIMENT TO SEE

15:04.470 --> 15:05.471
WHAT HAPPENS.

15:05.471 --> 15:06.239
>> Reporter: UNIVERSITY OF

15:06.239 --> 15:08.107
FLORIDA PROFESSOR PHIL LOUNIBOS

15:08.107 --> 15:09.542
HAS STUDIED MOSQUITOES AND THE

15:09.542 --> 15:12.011
DISEASES THEY CARRY FOR OVER 40

15:12.011 --> 15:13.045
YEARS.

15:13.045 --> 15:14.046
HE'S NOT INVOLVED WITH THE

15:14.046 --> 15:15.815
PROPOSED G.M. EXPERIMENT IN THE

15:15.815 --> 15:16.783
KEYS.

15:16.783 --> 15:18.117
>> WE BELIEVE, THOSE OF US WHO

15:18.117 --> 15:21.120
HAVE WORKED WITH MOSQUITOES,

15:21.120 --> 15:24.590
THAT THE PROBABILITY OF

15:24.590 --> 15:28.561
SOMETHING GOING WRONG IS NOT

15:28.561 --> 15:29.562
VERY HIGH.

15:29.562 --> 15:30.096
>> Reporter: LOUNIBOS IS

15:30.096 --> 15:31.230
CONVINCED THE TRIAL WOULD BE

15:31.230 --> 15:33.399
SAFE, BUT HE QUESTIONS ITS

15:33.399 --> 15:34.901
EFFECTIVENESS.

15:34.901 --> 15:36.235
HE SAYS OTHER MOSQUITO SPECIES

15:36.235 --> 15:38.271
CAN CARRY DENGUE, AND THE LOCAL

15:38.271 --> 15:40.406
BUGS COULD EVOLVE TO OUTSMART

15:40.406 --> 15:42.775
THE GENETICALLY MODIFIED MALES.

15:42.775 --> 15:44.644
>> IN THE ABSENCE OF DENGUE, THE

15:44.644 --> 15:46.813
ABSENCE OF A REALLY SIGNIFICANT

15:46.813 --> 15:48.548
THREAT OF DENGUE, I SEE THE

15:48.548 --> 15:54.287
OXITEC IMPLEMENTATION IN THE

15:54.287 --> 15:57.190
KEYS IN THE CONTEXT OF STRONG

15:57.190 --> 16:00.693
PUBLIC OPPOSITION TO BE

16:00.693 --> 16:01.861
INAPPROPRIATE.

16:01.861 --> 16:02.762
>> Reporter: GLOBALLY, DENGUE

16:02.762 --> 16:04.964
HAS SURGED 30-FOLD IN THE PAST

16:04.964 --> 16:06.666
50 YEARS, AND INCREASED TRAVEL

16:06.666 --> 16:08.634
FROM ENDEMIC AREAS ALONG WITH

16:08.634 --> 16:10.603
WARMER TEMPERATURES MEANS THE

16:10.603 --> 16:12.138
THREAT IS SPREADING.

16:12.138 --> 16:13.639
I ASKED DE MIER WHAT MIGHT

16:13.639 --> 16:15.274
HAPPEN IF SHE BLOCKS THE TRIAL

16:15.274 --> 16:16.943
AND THERE'S ANOTHER, MORE

16:16.943 --> 16:18.578
SERIOUS DENGUE OUTBREAK IN THE

16:18.578 --> 16:19.612
KEYS.

16:19.612 --> 16:20.513
DO YOU WORRY THAT SOMEONE WOULD

16:20.513 --> 16:22.381
CALL YOU UP AND SAY, "MILA, YOU

16:22.381 --> 16:23.983
STOOD IN THE WAY.

16:23.983 --> 16:24.817
YOU DID THIS"?

16:24.817 --> 16:25.618
DO YOU... DO YOU WORRY ABOUT

16:25.618 --> 16:26.319
THAT?

16:26.319 --> 16:27.053
>> NO.

16:27.053 --> 16:28.521
>> Reporter: WHY?

16:28.521 --> 16:29.488
>> NO, BECAUSE, TO BE HONEST

16:29.488 --> 16:32.592
WITH YOU, I THINK THE... THAT

16:32.592 --> 16:34.560
PEOPLE HAVE TO AGREE.

16:34.560 --> 16:37.263
AND AT THIS POINT, AGAIN, WE ARE

16:37.263 --> 16:39.899
FREE OF DENGUE FOR FIVE YEARS.

16:39.899 --> 16:42.235
WE ARE, I THINK, AS A CITIZEN,

16:42.235 --> 16:44.637
AS A MOTHER AND A TAXPAYER, I

16:44.637 --> 16:46.105
THINK THESE ARE MY RIGHTS, AND

16:46.105 --> 16:47.874
THE WHOLE COMMUNITY'S RIGHT TO

16:47.874 --> 16:48.708
CHOOSE.

16:48.708 --> 16:50.076
DO WE WANT TO BE PART OF THESE

16:50.076 --> 16:50.910
TESTS OR NO?

16:50.910 --> 16:51.777
>> Reporter: DID YOU EVER THINK,

16:51.777 --> 16:53.279
"MAYBE WE SHOULD JUST GO OUT AND

16:53.279 --> 16:55.314
GET EVERYBODY IN KEY HAVEN TO

16:55.314 --> 16:56.782
JUST SIGN A PIECE OF PAPER THAT

16:56.782 --> 16:58.317
SAYS 'I'M OKAY WITH THIS'"?

16:58.317 --> 16:58.918
>> EVERY PERSON?

16:58.918 --> 16:59.986
NO.

16:59.986 --> 17:00.920
BECAUSE THERE'S NO WAY YOU CAN

17:00.920 --> 17:02.421
GET 100% OF PEOPLE TO AGREE TO

17:02.421 --> 17:04.056
ANYTHING.

17:04.056 --> 17:05.825
THAT'S, YOU KNOW, PUTTING IN A

17:05.825 --> 17:07.360
ROAD, PUTTING A BRIDGE.

17:07.360 --> 17:08.794
YOU'VE GOT SOMEONE WHO'S GOING

17:08.794 --> 17:11.864
TO DISAGREE WITH IT.

17:11.864 --> 17:12.732
>> Reporter: THE F.D.A.'S CENTER

17:12.732 --> 17:14.667
FOR VETERINARY MEDICINE, WHICH

17:14.667 --> 17:16.102
APPROVES ANY GENETIC

17:16.102 --> 17:18.004
MODIFICATIONS TO ANIMALS, WILL

17:18.004 --> 17:20.006
HAVE THE FINAL SAY OVER WHETHER

17:20.006 --> 17:22.141
OR NOT THE OXITEC MOSQUITO TRIAL

17:22.141 --> 17:24.577
IN THE FLORIDA KEYS PROCEEDS.

17:24.577 --> 17:26.145
AN F.D.A. SPOKESPERSON TOLD US

17:26.145 --> 17:28.681
THERE'S NO TIMELINE FOR WHEN

17:28.681 --> 17:30.349
THAT MIGHT HAPPEN.

17:32.318 --> 17:33.286
>> Sreenivasan: FOR A CLOSER

17:33.286 --> 17:34.553
LOOK AT HOW SCIENTISTS ARE

17:34.553 --> 17:35.688
GENETICALLY MODIFYING

17:35.688 --> 17:37.590
MOSQUITOES, WATCH THE VIDEO ON

17:37.590 --> 17:38.758
OUR FACEBOOK PAGE AT

17:38.758 --> 17:41.193
www.facebook/com/newshour.

17:42.828 --> 17:43.829
>> Sreenivasan: FOR 15 YEARS,

17:43.829 --> 17:45.631
THE U.S.' WAR ON DRUGS IN

17:45.631 --> 17:47.533
COLOMBIA HAS RELIED ON CROP

