BUT THIS WEEK, COLUMBIA'S

17:51.771 --> 17:53.072
GOVERNMENT ANNOUNCED IT'S

17:53.072 --> 17:54.607
PHASING OUT THE U.S.-LED

17:54.607 --> 17:55.274
PROGRAM.

17:55.274 --> 17:56.142
SO, HOW WILL THIS SHIFT IN

17:56.142 --> 17:57.376
POLICY AFFECT THE RELATIONSHIP

17:57.376 --> 17:58.344
BETWEEN THE TWO COUNTRIES?

17:58.344 --> 17:59.412
JOINING ME VIA SKYPE FROM

